git clone git@github.com:boatd/boatd-opencpn.git

or 

sails-nmea-proxy

sails-ui


create a boatd config, set it to use 


running:
    run sailsd

    
set initial lat/lon and wind speed
	init_sails.sh 

    run boatd
    (optional) run sails-ui
    
    opencpn output:
		load opencpn
		add input on port 10110 UDP
		add output on port 10111 UDP
		run boatd-opencpn
		
    
		run collision detector
		python recvBoatData.py
   
    run behaviour:
		boatdctl behaviour-start example
		